beer.beer_description:
Written, directed & produced by Akasha & NZ Hops 102.

Starring soft tropicals, citrus, pine red fruit, candy.

Join Akasha as they invite you to take everything you know about hops and multiply it by NZH 102, in that time of year where desires are revealed, secrets are exposed, and chances are finally taken...

This holiday season, all you need is Hops, Actually.

items.badge_description: It's New Brew Thursday! Drink any beer you have never had before on three different Thursdays in a 20 day period.

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 105 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 22!

items.checkin_comment: Steady hazy, big of pine and soft citrus.
